track_title: Just the final crest from west

track_notes: This is one of the many way to reach the summit, not so cool in summertime, best in winter, good shoes and water needed
Climbing that way is reserved for fool people! This is not the right way but it is one of the many way to reach the summit
This way to climb the Mont Vial is not the good one, the path is very old and nobody uses it by this time! plenty room on summit for antenna.
track_title: Only for fool or mad people

track_notes:
From the village, use the normal way, after 1 hour walk, turn left to climb an easy crest and follow the path, can be snow on winter, and hot in summer.
Enjoy the panorama.
